@node "Document_9" "Path"
Here you can type the path for the actual conference.

@endnode

@node "Document_10" "Cycler"
Here  you  can  cycle  the  available  conferences.   its  nessecary to use
Cycle2Menu :)

@endnode

@node "Document_11" "Upload"
This Button selects the conference where the Upload-Path are valid.
@endnode

@node "Document_12" "Cancel"
Cancel the Configure Operation
@endnode

@node "Document_13" "Save"
Saves all chenges in the PROGDIR:
@endnode

@node "Document_14" "Pubscreen"
Here you can type the public screen where the autotrader should be opened.
@endnode

@node "Document_15" "FileReq"
This button opens a filerequester for selecting the Upload-Path
@endnode

